{
  "stem": "1918.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he-- when he picked us out-- first, they separated the men and the women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, my brother was taken with the men's side, and my-- we stayed too long trying to get the cigarettes, my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by the time we came down, my-- the women and men were selected-- by the time we jumped off the cattle car-- and ran after the group that my mother was going with, to see her, wherever she's going, just to see her.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know where she was going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just as we reached-- just as I saw the back of her head, Mengele went like this, [GERMAN], these two, my sister and I, and he took us to the life side.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they took us into this hideous place, what they called the disinfection, where they stripped us of our clothes, and shaved our head and pubic hair, and threw a rag at us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you were that big, you got a garment this small or vice versa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They just threw a rag at you after they shaved you, within seconds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything had to be so fast and it didn't matter if you were bleeding from the shaving.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nothing mattered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were in this huge, giant, wet place, and suddenly we looked over there and we saw two monsters that looked familiar, and it was my sister, Regina and Zippy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Evidently he took them to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He led them to the crematorium group, and at the crematorium he decided to make another selection.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Remember, he was-- he was the ruler of life and death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He could do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And usually made a ruling for death, not for life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he picked out Regina and Zippy, my two sisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
